    "Natural Family PlanningThis method involves tracking the menstrual cycle and avoiding sex during the fertile window.",
    "It requires careful monitoring and is less effective than other methods, with a typical failure rate of around 25%.It is important to note that there are benefits and risks associated with each contraceptive option, and the most effective method depends on individual circumstances and preferences.",
